messages.content: Silenda is here which is a rarity. He had pretty normal clothing on and his hair was in a ponytail. He was minding his own business, getting what he needed for quite some time so he wouldn't need to leave his house
And here we have Argenti
Looking for some damn chickie nuggies
He sees Argenti and tries to actively avoid him, already feeling tears start to well up.
Argenti slips because he didn't notice a wet floor sign. As he got up, he noticed someone familiar. "Wait, you're..."
He doesnt say anything and just tries to get away. He doesnt want to deal with this
Silver Chariot is already in front of him, rapier pointed at his neck. "Give me one reason I shouldn't kill you right here, right now."
"P-please ju-just ....le-leave me alone....." He whimpered, breaking down.
Argenti was caught off guard for a second, but remembered who he was dealing with. Or at least, who he THOUGHT he was dealing with.
"in the very least I should give you some ...payback."

"I-I dont wa-want to harm an-anyone....." He sniffled "I-I hate that I ever harmed anyone....I-Its why I hid away....I dont want to scare others....I just want to find the timeline where I took care of Trish and Doppio and I was a great father to them.....I miss that timeline I want to go back and just....saty forever so you guys dont have to be scared of me...." Dude was just....having a breakdown....How long bas it been since he really talked to another Mun?
Argenti's heart wanted to help him, but his brain kept screaming *Remember when he MAIMED YOU AND THREW YOU OFF A CLIFF TO DIE?!*
"Yeah. Sure."
//I know things are getting spicy but I should really sleep

"I-Im so sorry.....I-Ill leave you al-alone....Y-You wont see my fa-face and y-you wont have to worry...." He wiped his eyes "I only l-leave my house for fo-food..."

(Sleep well!)
Blood was dripping on the floor. Argenti was already counting
No time skip happened. "I vowed to n-never use my st-stand on others a-again...." He just....walked away...he was going to finish his shopping as fast as he could
Argenti was puzzled. But now he was bleeding, too. *what the hell?*
He felt horrible. He missed the good timeline so much....God it was going to be hard to stop crying now...
*lamia never acted like this and time hasn't shipped yet...* Argenti went after him
He was just trying to get what he need and fast. He was....still crying
Chariot, due to it's speed, caught up with him again. "Are you ok?" Argenti spoke through his stand

"......No....." He wiped his eyes "I feel horrible about what Ive done.....I had a change of heart after I was in the timeline where....I actually took care of Doppio and Trish.....I was....the happiest there...."
"I don't know who Doppio is, but it sounds like you've changed..."
"I-I could never bring my self to face the ones I hurt....Just....Just if you know anyone who ive hurt....Tell them Im sorry..."
"I'm sorry for threatening your life in a grocery store." Chariot gives the mun a small hug
"Its ok....you had every right too...."
"I may not remember any of the universes where you were a parent, but I'm proud of you."
That suprised him "......Really.....?"
@Iris

"y'know...maybe I could check out one of those universes you were talking about."

"I'm pretty sure a portal could be opening up now. you'd never know."
"Well then....I....I guess we should go look...?"
"Sure."
